---
title: Sweet-As-Honey Chicken with Snow Peas over Jasmine Rice
description: We all have a soft spot for the sticky-sweet chicken that’s a staple of takeout dinners. But it’s not exactly a meal for any night of the week—until now. We’re swapping out the heavy glaze for a fresh burst of ginger and a swirl of honey and soy sauce. Served with tender snow peas on a bed of jasmine rice, it’ll give you a good reason to toss the phone number for your delivery joint.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5a32a2c430a03b4f29290302-324cad72.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sweet-as-honey-chicken-5a32a2c430a03b4f29290302-4d62ccb2.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
servings: 2
